<div class='flex flex-col gap-4 lg:gap-6'>
  <div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
    <div class='grid gap-1'>
      <h1 class='font-heading text-2xl font-semibold dark:text-white'>Frequently
        Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class='text-base text-muted-foreground'>Find answers to common
        questions about our platform and services.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='space-y-6'>
    <!-- FAQ 1 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>What is the
        Accelerator Platform?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        The Accelerator Platform is an AI-powered tool designed to help
        entrepreneurs and startups build, launch, and scale their businesses.
        Our platform provides AI-driven recommendations, business planning
        tools, and resources to guide you through every stage of your startup
        journey.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 2 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>How do I create a new
        project?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        To create a new project, click on the "New Project" button in the left
        sidebar. You'll be prompted to enter your project name and description.
        Once created, you can start exploring AI-generated ideas, developing
        your business model, and building your startup strategy using our
        various tools.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 3 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>How does the AI
        assistant work?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Our AI assistant uses advanced machine learning models to analyze your
        project requirements and provide tailored recommendations. Simply
        describe your idea or ask specific questions, and our AI will generate
        insights, suggest improvements, and help you build various aspects of
        your business including business models, financial projections,
        marketing strategies, and team building.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 4 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>What are credits and
        how do they work?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Credits are our platform's currency system that allows you to access
        premium AI features and advanced tools. Each credit represents a certain
        amount of computational resources used for AI processing. Different
        features consume different amounts of credits, and you can purchase
        additional credits as needed. Free accounts receive a monthly credit
        allowance to get started.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 5 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>Can I collaborate
        with others on projects?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Yes! Our platform includes comprehensive collaboration features. You can
        invite team members to your projects, share documents, assign tasks, and
        work together in real-time. The collaboration hub provides chat, file
        sharing, task management, and team coordination tools to keep everyone
        aligned and productive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 6 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>Is my data secure?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Absolutely. We take data security very seriously. All data is encrypted
        in transit and at rest using industry-standard encryption protocols. We
        comply with GDPR and other privacy regulations, and we never share your
        personal information or project data with third parties without your
        explicit consent. Our infrastructure is hosted on secure,
        enterprise-grade cloud platforms with regular security audits.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 7 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>What types of
        businesses can I create with this platform?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Our platform is designed to support entrepreneurs across all industries
        and business types. Whether you're building a tech startup, e-commerce
        business, service-based company, or traditional brick-and-mortar
        venture, our AI tools can help. We support various business models
        including SaaS, marketplace, subscription services, and more. The AI
        adapts its recommendations based on your industry and target market.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 8 -->
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-3'>How accurate are the
        AI-generated business plans and financial projections?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Our AI generates comprehensive business plans and financial projections
        based on industry data, market trends, and proven business frameworks.
        While the AI provides excellent starting points and insights, we always
        recommend validating the information with real market research and
        professional advisors. The AI serves as a powerful tool to accelerate
        your planning process, but final business decisions should incorporate
        human expertise and local market knowledge.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Still Need Help? -->
  <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
    <div class='text-center'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2'>Still Need Help?</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
        Can't find the answer you're looking for? Our support team is here to
        help.
      </p>
      <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3'>
        <button
          class='flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-md hover:bg-primary/90'
        >
          {{lucide 'MessageCircle' 'w-4 h-4'}}
          Contact Support
        </button>
        <button
          class='flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-border rounded-md hover:bg-muted'
        >
          {{lucide 'ExternalLink' 'w-4 h-4'}}
          Community Forum
        </button>
        <button
          class='flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-border rounded-md hover:bg-muted'
        >
          {{lucide 'BookOpen' 'w-4 h-4'}}
          Documentation
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>